flowchart LR
    Client[Agent SDK Call] --> EvalAPI[/POST /api/v1/evaluate/]
    EvalAPI --> Identity[Agent identity + tool params]
    Identity --> Evaluator[OPAEvaluator]
    Evaluator --> Cache[(Redis eval cache)]
    Evaluator --> OPA[OPA subprocess eval]
    OPA --> Decision{Decision}
    Decision -->|allow/block/escalate| Audit[AuditEmitter]
    Audit --> AuditLog[(audit_log)]
    Decision --> Response[EvaluationResponse]
    OPA -->|timeout/error| Fallback[Fail-closed fallback]
    Fallback --> Audit
    Fallback --> Response
